name: bootstrap-material-design

scripts.build: npm run build:js && npm run build:js-min && npm run build:css && npm run build:css-min
scripts.docs:assets: node-sass --importer=node_modules/node-sass-tilde-importer assets/scss/docs.scss > assets/css/docs.css && cssnano assets/css/docs.css assets/css/docs.min.css
scripts.docs:deploy: npm run build && npm run docs:assets && npm run docs:compile && ./deploy.sh
scripts.watch:css: npm run build:css && npm run build:css -- --watch
